Version 1.0.0
-------------

- Initial release. A software implementation of the model described by
  Stevenson, Smit, and Setyawan (2026).

- Includes model fitting function `fit.morph()`; plotting function
  `plotmorph()`; simulation functions `sim.measurements()`,
  `sim.morph()`, and `extract.sim.morph()`; prediction function
  `predictblup()`; and S3 methods `plot.lme.morph()`,
  `predict.lme.morph()`, `summary.lme.morph()`.

- The data analysed in Stevenson, Smit, and Setyawan (2026) are
  available as the exported object `manta`.